            "summary_en": "Anyone who believes they have become a victim of an online financial scam, such as phishing, malware, or unauthorized bank transfers, should contact their bank or NSRC immediately.",
            "summary_ms": "Sesiapa yang percaya mereka menjadi mangsa penipuan kewangan dalam talian seperti phishing, perisian hasad atau pemindahan wang tanpa kebenaran perlu segera menghubungi bank atau NSRC.",
            "summary_zh": "任何怀疑自己遭遇网络金融诈骗（如网络钓鱼、恶意软件或未经授权的银行转账）的人，都应立即联系银行或 NSRC。",
            "title_en": "Who should contact NSRC?",
            "title_ms": "Siapakah yang perlu menghubungi NSRC?",
            "title_zh": "谁应该联系 NSRC？",
            "topic_code": "TOPIC-SCAMS"
